Basho quick demo.

To install:
virtualenv flask
pip install flask
pip install riak

To test the POST:
curl -i -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"sender":"Nicholas", "recipient":"Somebody"}' http://localhost:5000/message

HTTP/1.0 201 CREATED
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 109
Server: Werkzeug/0.10.4 Python/2.7.6
Date: Tue, 06 Oct 2015 20:53:10 GMT

{
  "message": {
    "body": "",
    "key": 0,
    "recipient": "Somebody",
    "sender": "Nicholas"
  }
}%

To test the GET:
curl -i http://localhost:5000/message/0

HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 109
Server: Werkzeug/0.10.4 Python/2.7.6
Date: Tue, 06 Oct 2015 20:58:25 GMT

{
  "message": {
    "body": "",
    "key": 0,
    "recipient": "Somebody",
    "sender": "Nicholas"
  }
}%

curl -i -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"key":0, "body":"Filler"}' http://localhost:5000/message/reply
HTTP/1.0 201 CREATED
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 146
Server: Werkzeug/0.10.4 Python/2.7.6
Date: Tue, 06 Oct 2015 23:53:45 GMT

{
  "message": {
    "body": "Filler\n-------\n|Reply|\n-------\n\n",
    "key": 1,
    "recipient": "Nicholas",
    "sender": "Somebody"
  }
}%
